NavMesh Information: 
You set agent type so entites can walk on agent type surface
Like for example if a zombie is an agent type humanoid it can only walk on surface with agent type surface
Agent stats won't affect the entitiy only Obstcale avoidnace will affect it

NavMesh Surface:
Radius: Distance away from unwalkable area that can't be walked
So like <unwalkable area><r><walkable area>

NavMesh Link:
Radius is the area where the entites can start using it.
Ex:   <radius>-link-<radius>
if an entity goes on the radius they can use the link
